'''大同與西安寶寶'''，（{{lang-en|Da Tung and Xi'an Bao Bao}}）是一件2002年的室外[[青銅雕塑|青銅雕塑]]展示作品，它的原意是「世界大同」（Universal Peace）和「象寶寶」（Baby Elephant）。它位於[[波特蘭_(俄勒岡州)|波特蘭]][[市中心|市中心]]的{{link-en|北公園區|North Park Blocks}}，<ref name=PAA>{{cite web|title=Da Tung and Xi'an Bao Bao (Universal Peace and Baby Elephant)|url=http://www.publicartarchive.org/work/da-tung-and-xian-bao-bao-universal-peace-and-baby-elephant#date|publisher=Public Art Archive|accessdate=September 24, 2014}}</ref>創作者不明。<ref name=SI>{{cite web|title=Da Tung and Xi'an Bao Bao, (sculpture)|url=http://collections.si.edu/search/results.htm?q=record_ID:siris_ari_368977|publisher=[[Smithsonian_Institution|Smithsonian Institution]]|accessdate=September 25, 2014|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303201533/http://collections.si.edu/search/results.htm?q=record_ID:siris_ari_368977|dead-url=no}}</ref>它是[[姆尔特诺默县|姆尔特诺默县]]和波特蘭市的{{link-en|區域藝術文化委員會|Regional Arts & Culture Council}}的「公共藝術禮遇收藏」計畫的一部份。

== 簡述 ==
這件青銅雕塑由中國[[西安|西安]]的「五環鑄造廠」（Five Rings Bronze Foundry）製造，於2002年被安置在北公園區的西北公園大道（Northwest Park Avenue）與西伯恩賽德街（West Burnside Street）交會處。<ref name=RACC>{{cite web|title=Check out public art this summer: What are YOUR five favorites?|url=http://racc.org/public-art/check-out-public-art-summer-what-are-your-five-favorites|publisher=[[Regional_Arts_&_Culture_Council|Regional Arts & Culture Council]]|accessdate=September 25, 2014|date=May 30, 2014|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006083734/http://racc.org/public-art/check-out-public-art-summer-what-are-your-five-favorites|archivedate=2014年10月6日}}</ref>量出的尺寸是{{Convert|135|in|m}} x {{Convert|77|in|m}} x {{Convert|168|in|m}}，特徵是一隻年輕的小象在大的成象之上。<ref name=DaTung>{{cite web|title=Da Tung and Xi’an Bao Bao (Universal Peace and Baby Elephant)|url=http://racc.org/public-art/search/?page=details&skip=0&sort_pref=sort_title&results_per_page=9&search_title=Da%20Tung%20and%20Xi’an%20Bao%20Bao&search_artist=&search_keyword=&search_other=&search_collection=&search_discipline=&search=Search|publisher=Regional Arts & Culture Council|accessdate=September 25, 2014|archive-date=2016-09-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160920235741/https://racc.org/public-art/search/?page=details&skip=0&sort_pref=sort_title&results_per_page=9&search_title=Da%20Tung%20and%20Xi%E2%80%99an%20Bao%20Bao&search_artist=&search_keyword=&search_other=&search_collection=&search_discipline=&search=Search|dead-url=no}}</ref>作品由兩個名字組成：「大同」（Da Tung），也可翻譯為世界和平（universal peace）或「大銅」（large bronze）；和西安寶寶（Xi'an Bao Bao），意指象寶寶（baby elephant）。<ref name=PAA/>

這件複製品是從[[商朝|商朝]]晚期（[[大約|大約]][[公元前|公元前]]1200–1100年）的[[酒器|酒器]]得到灵感，由霍保柱（Huo Baozhu）捐赠，<ref name=DaTung/> 大約比原品大16倍。<ref name=PAA/>現已絕種的[[中國象|中國象]] （{{lang-en|Elephas maximus rubridens}}）活動地區北至[[河南|河南]][[安陽|安陽]]，公元前十四世紀時[[廣西|廣西]]還有中國象。<ref name="Brown2011">{{cite book|author=Robin Brown|title=Blood Ivory: The Massacre of the African Elephant|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=i7cTDQAAQBAJ&pg=PT12|date=2011-110-8|publisher=History Press| isbn=978-0-7524-7530-1| page=12|language=en}}</ref>

